query: SELECT ml.id, ml.status, ml.products_found, ml.new_restocks, ml.duration_ms, ml.created_at, r.name as region_name FROM monitoring_logs ml LEFT JOIN regions r ON ml.region_id = r.id ORDER BY ml.created_at DESC LIMIT 3
